' @id(SEQ-DIAGRAMS-FIRST)
' @ref(USE-DIAGRAMS-FIRST)
' @desc(SEQ-DIAGRAMS-FIRST, "Objective flow for the diagrams-first reading-order directive carried in the CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md managed block (CMP-ENTRYPOINT-DIRECTIVE). After the session brief gives the freshness verdict (DOM-SESSION-CONTEXT), the agent branches: FRESH -> trust the diagrams, read them and follow trace.yml source_links to the code, then act; STALE -> run /mdd-map on the drifted area (named by the map_status drift list) FIRST to re-sync current/, then read. This is the canonical reading order new mdd init projects ship with.")
' Objective sequence: the reading-order algorithm the entrypoint directive encodes.
title Diagrams-first reading order (objective)

actor "Agent" as Agent <<missing>>
participant "mdd context\nverdict" as Verdict
participant ".mdd/models + trace.yml\nsource_links" as Diagrams
participant "/mdd-map\n(re-derive current)" as Map
participant "code" as Code

Agent -> Verdict : freshness from session brief
alt FRESH
  Verdict --> Agent : diagrams trusted
  Agent -> Diagrams : read concept diagrams
  Agent -> Code : follow source_links, then act
else STALE (drift list)
  Verdict --> Agent : drifted model_ids
  Agent -> Map : /mdd-map the drifted area FIRST
  Map --> Diagrams : current/ re-synced
  Agent -> Diagrams : now read trusted diagrams
end
@enduml
